{"ticker": "BYDDY", "company": "BYD CO LTD-UNSPONSORED ADR", "weight_sum": 1.07, "etfs": ["ARKQ"], "is_private": false, "query": "($BYDDY OR \"Byd Co Ltd-unsponsored Adr\") -is:retweet min_faves:10 since_time:1777646987 until_time:1777654642", "n_fetched": 1, "n_kept": 1, "n_dropped": 0, "kept": [{"type": "tweet", "id": "2050204102030688333", "url": "https://x.com/WallStDiaries/status/2050204102030688333", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/WallStDiaries/status/2050204102030688333", "text": "$BYDDY\nBYD\u2019nin \u0130lk \u00c7eyrek K\u00e2r\u0131nda %55\u2019lik Sert D\u00fc\u015f\u00fc\u015f\n\nBYD, 2026 y\u0131l\u0131n\u0131n ilk \u00e7eyre\u011finde net k\u00e2r\u0131n\u0131n ge\u00e7en y\u0131l\u0131n ayn\u0131 d\u00f6nemine g\u00f6re %55 oran\u0131nda azalarak yakla\u015f\u0131k 4,08 milyar yuana (598 milyon dolar) geriledi\u011fini bildirdi. \n\n\u00c7in i\u00e7 pazar\u0131nda elektrikli ara\u00e7lara y\u00f6nelik vergi muafiyetlerinin Ocak ay\u0131nda yar\u0131ya indirilmesi ve Xiaomi ile Geely gibi rakiplerin dahil oldu\u011fu agresif fiyat sava\u015flar\u0131, \u015firketin k\u00e2r marjlar\u0131n\u0131 ciddi \u015fekilde bask\u0131lad\u0131. \u015eirketin toplam geliri de i\u00e7 pazardaki talebin zay\u0131flamas\u0131yla %12'lik bir d\u00fc\u015f\u00fc\u015f ya\u015fad\u0131.\n\n\u0130\u00e7 pazardaki %24'l\u00fck sat\u0131\u015f kayb\u0131na ra\u011fmen, BYD'nin k\u00fcresel stratejisi umut vaat etmeye devam ediyor. Mart 2026 itibar\u0131yla ihracat rakamlar\u0131, y\u00fcksek k\u00fcresel enerji maliyetlerinin etkisiyle ge\u00e7en y\u0131la g\u00f6re %65 artarak 120 bin arac\u0131 a\u015ft\u0131. \u015eirket, 2026 y\u0131l\u0131 i\u00e7in ihracat hedefini 1,5 milyon araca y\u00fckseltirken, Macaristan ve Brezilya'daki yeni fabrikalar\u0131n devreye girmesiyle maliyetleri d\u00fc\u015f\u00fcrmeyi planl\u0131yor. \n\nAnalistler, Pekin Otomobil Fuar\u0131'nda tan\u0131t\u0131lan ve 1.000 km menzil sunan yeni nesil Blade Bataryal\u0131 modellerin, y\u0131l\u0131n ikinci yar\u0131s\u0131nda talebi yeniden canland\u0131rabilece\u011fini \u00f6ng\u00f6r\u00fcyor.", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 0, "replyCount": 0, "likeCount": 12, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 964, "createdAt": "Fri May 01 13:22:03 +0000 2026", "lang": "tr", "bookmarkCount": 0, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2050204102030688333", "displayTextRange": [0, 273], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "WallStDiaries", "url": "https://x.com/WallStDiaries", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/WallStDiaries", "id": "1856355605960654848", "name": "Wall Street G\u00fcnl\u00fckleri", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1992607305070759936/TxOzCOgu_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1856355605960654848/1763910045", "description": "", "location": "", "followers": 27054, "following": 547, "status": "", "canDm": true, "canMediaTag": false, "createdAt": "Tue Nov 12 15:17:36 +0000 2024", "entities": {"description": {"urls": []}, "url": {}}, "fastFollowersCount": 0, "favouritesCount": 22293, "hasCustomTimelines": true, "isTranslator": false, "mediaCount": 11451, "statusesCount": 24507, "withheldInCountries": [], "affiliatesHighlightedLabel": {}, "possiblySensitive": false, "pinnedTweetIds": [], "profile_bio": {"description": "ABD Borsalar\u0131ndaki \u015firketlerden en g\u00fcncel haberler.\n\nhttps://t.co/FCT815Du2c\nhttps://t.co/jAJC3PKC8q", "entities": {"description": {"urls": [{"display_url": "youtube.com/@WallStDiaries", "expanded_url": "http://youtube.com/@WallStDiaries", "indices": [53, 76], "url": "https://t.co/FCT815Du2c"}, {"display_url": "creators.spotify.com/pod/profile/wa\u2026", "expanded_url": "https://creators.spotify.com/pod/profile/wallstdiaries/", "indices": [77, 100], "url": "https://t.co/jAJC3PKC8q"}]}, "url": {"urls": [{"display_url": 